---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="FAQ - Echo4Ever" description="Frequently asked questions about Echo4Ever. Learn about plans, file types, privacy, legacy planning and more.">

  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      <p>Everything you need to know about Echo4Ever.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center;">

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Can I change my plan later?</h3>
        <p class="text-secondary">Absolutely. Upgrade or downgrade at any time from your account settings. Changes are prorated - you only pay the difference.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>What file types can I upload?</h3>
        <p class="text-secondary">Photos (JPG, PNG, GIF), videos (MP4, MOV), audio (MP3, M4A, WAV) and documents (PDF, DOC, DOCX). Up to 500 MB per file.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Who can see my memories?</h3>
        <p class="text-secondary">Only you - unless you choose to share. Every memory starts private. There are no public profiles, no social feeds and no algorithms.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>What is a Heritage Custodian?</h3>
        <p class="text-secondary">Someone you trust to manage your digital legacy. When the time comes, they can activate your account so the memories you've chosen are shared with the people you've named.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Can I cancel any time?</h3>
        <p class="text-secondary">Yes. No contracts, no penalties. Cancel from your account settings and you'll keep access until the end of your billing period.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-banner">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Still have questions?</h2>
      <p>We're here to help. Reach out any time.</p>
      <a href="mailto:contact@echo4ever.com" class="btn btn--primary btn--large">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>

<style>
  .faq-item {
    padding: 24px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .faq-item:first-of-type {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .faq-item h3 {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-size: var(--font-size-subheading);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .faq-item p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2vw, 24px);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
</style>
